        <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">Features</h1>
        <p class="govuk-body">The architecture catalogue provides a means of recording, updating and sharing information about the technology components used across the NICS to deliver deliver digital solutions and services. The catalogue provides the following functions:</p>
        <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
          <li><a class="govuk-link" href="#smart-search">Smart search</a></li>
          <li><a class="govuk-link" href="#browse-catalogue">Browse catalogue</a></li>
          <li><a class="govuk-link" href="#crud-entries">Add, update and remove catalogue entries</a></li>
          <li><a class="govuk-link" href="#link-entries">Link catalogue entries</a></li>
          <li><a class="govuk-link" href="#roles-and-permissions">Change user roles and permissions</a></li>
        </ul>

