        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m" id="smart-search">Smart search</h2>
        <p class="govuk-body">You can search the catalogue by entering a search word or phrase. You must enter at least three characters and your search will try to find entries that have the word or phrase you supplied in any of the enntry data items.</p>

        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m" id="browse-catalogue">Browse catalogue</h2>
        <p class="govuk-body">You can browse the entire catalogue and apply filters on either <strong>status</strong> and <strong>category/sub-category</strong> to produced a more specific list of entries. Detailed information can be found on each entry by following the view link.</p>

        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m" id="crud-entries">Add, update and remove catalogue entries</h2>
        <p class="govuk-body">If you are a contributor you can add, update and remove catalogue entries.</p>

        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m" id="link-entries">Link catalogue entries</h2>
        <p class="govuk-body">Entries can be linked to others entries via a 'depends on' relationship. When a entry is viewed you will see it's dependencies and what other entries are dependent upon it.</p>

        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m" id=>Change user roles and permissions</h2>
        <p class="govuk-body">Administrators can change user roles and assign other administrators.</p>
